&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A 24/7 virtual care team&lt;/strong&gt; to support our patients and take pressure off the floor team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-functional collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;—you’ll work with medical, operations, recruiting, and support teams who &lt;em&gt;actually&lt;/em&gt; work together.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An organization that evolves&lt;/strong&gt;—we’re building the future, and you’ll help shape it.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
